title: Anthropic And Databricks Team Up To Help Customers Launch Their Own AI Agents
body: The deal will bring flagship model Claude, to thousands of corporate customers, including Comcast, Conde Nast and Block.

title: Anthropic, Databricks Team Up in Scramble for AI Revenue
body: Anthropic and Databricks struck a five year, $100 million pact to sell artificial intelligence tools to businesses, targeting those seeking to build their own AI agents.
